e EXIT_CODE=0 without sandbox)\n   - ✅ Pre-release commit of 37 accumulated files\n   - 🔄 Phase 2: Inventory audit complete — found 3 discrepancies, all in hooks count (README/WORKFLOW-GUIDE show 11, filesystem has 25)\n   - 🔄 Phase 3: Docs sync IN PROGRESS — need to fix hook count and list in README.md line 32 and WORKFLOW-GUIDE.md\n\n   The 25 template hooks are: circuit-breaker, cli-health, config-change-audit, context-freshness, context-loader, context-monitor, context-reinforcement, file-index, mcp-health, memory-recall, notify, permission-denied-log, post-compact-restore, post-edit-lint, post-tool-failure-log, pre-compact-state, protect-files, spec-stop-guard, subagent-start, subagent-stop, task-completed-gate, tdd-checker, tool-redirect, transcript-ingest, update-check\n\n9. Optional Next Step:\n   Continue the `/release` Phase 3 docs sync. Fix README.md line 32:\n\n   Current: `| **Hooks** | 11 hooks — context-loader, protect-and-breaker, post-edit-lint, update-check, memory-recall, notify, config-change-audit, task-completed-gate, post-tool-failure-log, transcript-ingest, pre-compact |`\n\n   Needs to become: `| **Hooks** | 25 hooks — context-loader, protect-and-breaker, post-edit-lint, update-check, memory-recall, notify, config-change-audit, task-completed-gate, post-tool-failure-log, transcript-ingest, pre-compact-state, circuit-breaker, cli-health, context-freshness, context-monitor, context-reinforcement, file-index, mcp-health, permission-denied-log, post-compact-restore, protect-files, spec-stop-guard, subagent-start, subagent-stop, tdd-checker, tool-redirect |`\n\n   Then update WORKFLOW-GUIDE.md with the same count correction, then proceed to Phase 4 (version bump to v2.0.8), Phase 5 (Slack message), Phase 6 (commit + tag).\n</summary>"}
