lation\" \\\n    \"no\"; then\n    tui_step \"Wechsel zu npm...\"\n    if brew uninstall --cask claude-code 2>&1 | tail -3; then\n      if npm install -g @anthropic-ai/claude-code@latest 2>&1 | tail -3; then\n        tui_success \"Claude Code via npm installiert\"\n      else\n        tui_warn \"npm-Installation fehlgeschlagen. Manuell: npm i -g @anthropic-ai/claude-code@latest\"\n      fi\n    else\n      tui_warn \"Brew-Deinstallation fehlgeschlagen. Manuell: brew uninstall --cask claude-code\"\n    fi\n  fi\n}\n```\n\n**Detection Methods:**\n- Line 220: `brew list --cask claude-code` - direct cask check\n- Line 222: Path inspection for `/homebrew/` or `/Caskroom/` markers\n\n**Update Commands Executed:**\n- Line 235: `brew uninstall --cask claude-code` - remove Homebrew version\n- Line 236: `npm install -g @anthropic-ai/claude-code@latest` - install npm version\n\n---\n\n### 2. **Claude Code Version Check and Auto-Update** (`/Users/deniskern/Sites/npx-ai-setup/lib/setup.sh`)\n\n**File:** `/Users/deniskern/Sites/npx-ai-setup/lib/setup.sh`  \n**Lines:** 247-284\n\nFunction: `_check_claude_code_version()`\n```bash\n_check_claude_code_version() {\n  local MIN_CC_VERSION=\"2.1.89\"\n  local cc_version\n  cc_version=$(claude --version 2>/dev/null | head -1 | grep -oE '[0-9]+\\.[0-9]+\\.[0-9]+' | head -1)\n  [ -z \"$cc_version\" ] && return 0\n\n  # Semver comparison: returns 0 if $1 >= $2\n  _semver_ge() {\n    local IFS=.\n    local i a=($1) b=($2)\n    for ((i=0; i<3; i++)); do\n      [ \"${a[i]:-0}\" -gt \"${b[i]:-0}\" ] && return 0\n      [ \"${a[i]:-0}\" -lt \"${b[i]:-0}\" ] && return 1\n    done\n    return 0\n  }\n\n  if _semver_ge \"$cc_version\" \"$MIN_CC_VERSION\"; then\n    return 0\n  fi\n\n  tui_warn \"Claude Code v${cc_version} ist veraltet (Hooks benötigen >= v${MIN_CC_VERSION})\"\n  if ask_yes_no_menu \\\n    \"Claude Code jetzt aktualisieren?\" \\\n    \"Ja\" \"npm i -g @anthropic-ai/claude-code@latest\" \\\n    \"Nein\" \"Weiter ohne Update (einige Hooks funktionieren nicht)\" \\\n    \"no\"; then\n    tui_step \"Updating Claude Code...\"\n    if npm install -g @anthropic-ai/claude-code@latest 2>&1 | tail -3; then\n      local new_version\n      new_version=$(claude --version 2>/dev/null | head -1 | grep -oE '[0-9]+\\.[0-9]+\\.[0-9]+' | head -1)\n      tui_success \"Claude Code aktualisiert auf v${new_version:-latest}\"\n    else\n      tui_warn \"Update fehlgeschlagen. Manuell: npm i -g @anthropic-ai/claude-code@latest\"\n    fi\n  fi\n}\n```\n\n**Minimum Version:** Line 249: `2.1.89`  \n**Update Command:** Line 276: `npm install -g @anthropic-ai/claude-code@latest`  \n**Semver Comparison:** Lines 255-263\n\n---\n\n### 3. **Setup Script Integration** (`/Users/deniskern/Sites/npx-ai-setup/lib/setup.sh`)\n\n**File:** `/Users/deniskern/Sites/npx-ai-setup/lib/setup.sh`  \n**Lines:** 154-211\n\nFunction: `check_requirements()`\n```bash\n# Claude Code installation method check (brew has limitations)\nif [ \"$AI_CLI\" = \"claude\" ]; then\n  _check_claude_code_install_method    # Line 208\n  _check_claude_code_version            # Line 209\nfi\n```\n\nThis function is called during setup initialization to detect and migrate Claude Code.\n\n---\n\n### 4. **AI-Setup Version Check and Update** (`/Users/deniskern/Sites/npx-ai-setup/lib/update.sh`)\n\n**File:** `/Users/deniskern/Sites/npx-ai-setup/lib/update.sh`  \n**Lines:** 7-71\n\nFunction: `show_cli_update_notice()`\n- Checks for newer ai-setup versions via npm registry (line 36) or GitHub API (lines 44-56)\n- Uses 6-hour cache at `/tmp/ai-setup-cli-latest-version.txt` (line 14)\n- Semver comparison (line 65): `_semver_gt \"$latest\" \"$current\"`\n\n**Update Command:** Line 69: `npx github:onedot-digital-crew/npx-ai-setup`\n\n---\n\n### 5. **Version Metadata Functions** (`/Users/deniskern/Sites/npx-ai-setup/lib/core.sh`)\n\n**File:** `/Users/deniskern/Sites/npx-ai-setup/lib/core.sh`  \n**Lines:** 86-111\n\n```bash\n# Semver greater-than comparison\n_semver_gt() {\n  local -a a b\n  IFS=. read -ra a <<< \"$1\"\n  IFS=. read -ra b <<< \"$2\"\n  for i in 0 1 2; do\n    local ai=${a[$i]:-0} bi=${b[$i]:-0}\n    [ \"$ai\" -gt \"$bi\" ] 2>/dev/null && return 0\n    [ \"$ai\" -lt \"$bi\" ] 2>/dev/null && return 1\n  done\n  return 1  # equal\n}\n\nget_package_version() {\n  _json_read \"$SCRIPT_DIR/package.json\" '.version' 2>/dev/null || echo \"unknown\"\n}\n\nget_installed_version() {\n  if [ -f .ai-setup.json ] && _json_valid .ai-setup.json; then\n    _json_read .ai-setup.json '.version' || echo \"\"\n  else\n    echo \"\"\n  fi\n}\n```\n\n---\n\n### 6. **Project Update Flow** (`/Users/deniskern/Sites/npx-ai-setup/lib/update.sh`)\n\n**File:** `/Users/deniskern/Sites/npx-ai-setup/lib/update.sh`  \n**Lines:** 75-188\n\nFunction: `handle_version_check()` - triggers update/reinstall flows based on version comparison:\n- Same version: offers file sync or regeneration (lines 85-95)\n- Different version: offers migration or full reinstall (lines 135-147)\n\n---\n\n### **Key Update Commands Summary:**\n\n| Tool | Update Command | Location |\n|------|---|---|\n| **Claude Code (npm)** | `npm install -g @anthropic-ai/claude-code@latest` | lib/setup.sh:236, 276 |\n| **Claude Code (from Homebrew)** | `brew uninstall --cask claude-code` (first) | lib/setup.sh:235 |\n| **ai-setup** | `npx github:onedot-digital-crew/npx-ai-setup` | lib/update.sh:69 |\n| **npm packages (general)** | `npm install -g @package@latest` | lib/cli-tools.sh:73 |"}
