oss-Platform-Benachrichtigungen (Notification)\n- `mcp-health.sh` - MCP-Status-Check (SessionStart)\n- `config-change-audit.sh` - Settings-Änderungen loggen (ConfigChange)\n- `transcript-ingest.sh` - Session-Erfassung vor Stop (Stop)\n- `subagent-start/stop.sh` - Subagent-Lifecycle (SubagentStart/Stop)\n- etc. (27 insgesamt)\n\n**Hook-README Location:**\n`/Users/deniskern/Sites/npx-ai-setup/templates/claude/hooks/README.md`\n\n---\n\n## 3. settings.json Hook-Konfiguration - Beispiele\n\n**Template-Konfiguration:**\n`/Users/deniskern/Sites/npx-ai-setup/templates/claude/settings.json`\n\n**Hooks-Config-Struktur:**\n\n```json\n{\n  \"hooks\": {\n    \"SessionStart\": [\n      {\n        \"hooks\": [\n          {\n            \"type\": \"command\",\n            \"command\": \"bash \\\"${CLAUDE_PROJECT_DIR:-.}\\\"/.claude/hooks/context-reinforcement.sh\",\n            \"timeout\": 5000\n          },\n          {\n            \"type\": \"command\",\n            \"command\": \"bash \\\"${CLAUDE_PROJECT_DIR:-.}\\\"/.claude/hooks/context-loader.sh\",\n            \"timeout\": 5\n          }\n        ]\n      },\n      {\n        \"matcher\": \"compact\",\n        \"hooks\": [\n          {\n            \"type\": \"command\",\n            \"command\": \"bash \\\"${CLAUDE_PROJECT_DIR:-.}\\\"/.claude/hooks/post-compact-restore.sh\",\n            \"timeout\": 5\n          }\n        ]\n      }\n    ],\n    \"UserPromptSubmit\": [\n      {\n        \"hooks\": [\n          {\n            \"type\": \"command\",\n            \"command\": \"\\\"${CLAUDE_PROJECT_DIR:-.}\\\"/.claude/hooks/context-freshness.sh\",\n            \"timeout\": 5\n          },\n          {\n            \"type\": \"command\",\n            \"command\": \"\\\"${CLAUDE_PROJECT_DIR:-.}\\\"/.claude/hooks/update-check.sh\",\n            \"timeout\": 5\n          }\n        ]\n      }\n    ],\n    \"PreToolUse\": [\n      {\n        \"matcher\": \"Edit|Write\",\n        \"hooks\": [\n          {\n            \"type\":